{"tid":1389710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[強烈譴責］暴徒颱風 衝擊香港 破壞經濟","createTime":"2019-07-31T03:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T07:58:45.000Z","uid":18577,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"73f16b42afe58570eea8db9d6a72560c072c87cc","tid":1389710,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:17:15.000Z","msg":"本人嚴正要求<br />\n暴徒颱風立即撤離香港，比一眾盡忠職守返工大過天嘅職員可以繼續返工<br />\n<br />\n大家都唔好比暴徒颱風嚇到，應該繼續留守係公司上班，為香港經濟出份力，證明你哋唔係口講愛國愛港，請你哋用行動去表達<br />\n<br />\n同時，你哋繼續上班嘅精神一定可以打動到暴徒，令佢生生世世都唔敢再黎香港，搞亂香港經濟，影響個班香港人生計<br />\n<br />\n譴責暴徒 你我有責<br />\n<br />\n希望各位可以學下周生<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EyLjfOu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEyLjfOu.png&h=6e2840ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83d4acb612d978bfa63ae20e3f740c50ec512cb1","tid":1389710,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:18:14.000Z","msg":"頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又又又開錯台<br />\n今次應該開去創意台先岩"},{"pid":"38daf5c8ba0313cde23522891c5ffa5f2af94f74","tid":1389710,"uid":108571,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:23:16.000Z","msg":"有無人識佢<br />\n叫佢勤力啲打風都咪撚收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ea08456295101a90d1d284a8de043b10f20607","tid":1389710,"uid":18577,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"暴徒亂港<br />\n會為香港帶來前所未有嘅衝擊<br />\n<br />\n以下附上暴徒衝擊香港惡行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比掟磚可恥百萬倍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J1CQ6WT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ1CQ6WT.png&h=3d3de11e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比起立法會外嘅玻璃破壞程度難以估計<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKLbRoQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKLbRoQ.png&h=62230e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U1BB2vw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU1BB2vw.png&h=4a32d40e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比起開下滅火筒/水喉，暴徒直頭黎個大水災<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wRyQnvR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwRyQnvR.png&h=9510e4df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比起破壞警車，暴徒係無差別連校車都唔放過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aHo8TBD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaHo8TBD.png&h=fb5c08db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d547fc57c5f2af6528eebbd04f933842970cbf7","tid":1389710,"uid":18577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"38daf5c8ba0313cde23522891c5ffa5f2af94f74","tid":1389710,"uid":108571,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:23:16.000Z","msg":"有無人識佢<br />\n叫佢勤力啲打風都咪撚收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:25:12.000Z","msg":"推到周生同事上黎講下周生今日係咪留守公司啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c03695d08826bc6ad7c3eafb72d27ab48fe62e","tid":1389710,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1847cf9d0189fd1e9ccc1dc218ad58288aebab","tid":1389710,"uid":275607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:26:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2667df59d815bbd473b21c1737a10968c10121b","tid":1389710,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:26:33.000Z","msg":"譴責暴徒<br />\n你我有責"},{"pid":"afd72c3d5342bb125fb21b269cda6a4175700b70","tid":1389710,"uid":59854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:26:42.000Z","msg":"強列譴責韋柏衝擊香港"},{"pid":"1d8b64e9e651e1b2469f9a1eb0cbcdf7cf4ce79d","tid":1389710,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc